00213                fsal_status_t _struct_status_ = FSAL_STATUS_NO_ERROR ;          \
00214                (_struct_status_).major = (_code_) ;                            \
00215                (_struct_status_).minor = (_minor_) ;                           \

00226                        label_fsal_err(_code_), msg_fsal_err(_code_), _minor_); \
